道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"226099e940aae852b949d79336f7010683cc52f4","tid":2074619,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T11:25:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c73ff4c1d7432177dbd6d64056dae7ccd9a7c7e","tid":2074619,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T11:27:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}